## Program 5:

**Consider the following class:**

public class A{

public void sayHello(String name){

System.out.println(“Welcome :”);

try{

Thread.sleep(2000);

}catch(Exception e){

e.printStackTrace();

}

System.out.println(name);

}

}

- **Call the above sayHello method of a single A class object from the 3 threads in such a way
	 that we should get the regular output**